:: intro1 [nobr]
<<set $prevpass to "landing">>
<<set $pass to "intro1">>
<<set $nextpass to "introMoveOn">>

<<include "_templateIntro">>


:: intro1-text [nobr]
<p>Welcome to the Arthur Conan Doyle Trail. </p>
<p>You will be exploring the library with a group - do stay with them. </p>
/
<p>You should be able to hear my voice - if not you should put the volume up. </p>
/
<p>You will be asked to find information in the Library. </p>
<p>We are only able to go on this trail if we are quiet throughout the Library.</p>
/
<p>There will be points that you need to wait for confirmation from your group leader to move on – as we are playing through this as a group and you might need to wait for others to catch up. </p>
/
<p>Your screen will show an image with a London Library seal on it – when you see this wait for the thumbs up from </p>
/
<p>Let’s try that now. </p>





<<timed $btnAppearTime>>
    <<append "#btnContainer">>
    <<button "SEAL">>
            <<goto $nextpass>>
        <</button>>
        /* <<include "navbuttons">> */
    <</append>>
<</timed>>




