:: scene4-text [nobr]
<p class="bold">Scene 4 </p>

<<timed 3s>>
    <p>Head back down one flight of stairs to the Green Door that says ‘Back Stacks: Level 4’</p>

<p>You are looking for Geology/Science</p>

<p>When there, find ‘Man as a Geological Agent’ – it might be closer to the ‘Gold’ Section. When you find it, put your notepad on the book.</p>

    <</timed>>
/* END OF PASSAGE  */



